            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Fundanius <lb n="2"/>Optatus <lb n="3"/>saenator <note>sic</note> populi <lb n="4"/>Romani regio<lb break="no" n="5"/>nis possessor <lb n="6"/>domino Herculi <lb n="7"/>templum restituit recio <note>sic</note> <lb n="8"/>Auffeeiana <note>sic</note> felix et tu
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftfeld in Form einer tabula ansata. Der Dedikant ist sonst nicht bekannt. (B): AE 1984: Z. 8: Auffeiana. Mosaik.</p>
            </div>
